des:
Lite Bulb Moments products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light.

There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.
After connecting Alexa to your Lite Bulb Moments products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Lite Bulb Moments" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Lite Bulb Moments account in our "Lite Bulb Moments" app;
(3). You need to have some Lite Bulb Moments devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Lite Bulb Moments" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Lite Bulb Moments" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Lite Bulb Moments" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Lite Bulb Moments", and you'll be navigated to Lite Bulb Moments login page;
(9). Input your Lite Bulb Moments account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
